= Extremum Tool
:page-en: tools/Extremum
ifdef::env-github[:imagesdir: /en/modules/ROOT/assets/images]

Activate the tool, then select a function to find its local extrema. GeoGebra finds all the local estrema of polynomial functions, while for all the other functions it finds only the extrema belonging to the visible interval of the _Graphics View_.

[NOTE]
====

See also xref:/commands/Extremum.adoc[Extremum] command.

====
